Description: In Windows 8.1 with Update includes improvements that make Windows more familiar and convenient for devices with a mouse and touch input, as well as ensure availability of Windows on a wider range of devices providing you with additional choices.

Inside:
Includes one image 32-bit and 64-bit editions Windows 8.1
Build based on the original images MSDN (8 April 2014) and includes all the English editions of Windows 8.1:
- Single Language Windows 8.1 x86
